cdata.name: PoolStamp
cdata.desc: PoolStamp is a Proof of Stake cryptocurrency based on the x13 algorithm. It had a 5 day Proof of Work stage in which 4 millions XSP were mined. PoolStamp is backed by a profit switching cloud multipool which mines BTC and major Altcoins to convert them into XSP. Holders recieve rewards from the PoS nature of the coin and from the market support generated by cloud mining multipool.
